<div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-RSP_K25.html">RSP_K25</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The following trigger event is served by the following Conformance Statement: Another application determines a need for Personnel data about a person and sends a query to a system providing this information.</p>
</div>
